msgid "A practical workspace for trusted service providers."
msgstr "Фазои кории амалӣ барои мутахассисони боэътимод."

#: accounts/templates/accounts/partials/marketplace_sections.html:225
msgid ""
"Professionals can use the same account system today, with the interface "
"prepared for requests, offers, schedules, jobs, reviews, and service history "
"as the marketplace grows."
