#: accounts/templates/accounts/partials/marketplace_sections.html:245
msgid ""
"Email verification helps keep repair requests and service activity connected "
"to the correct account."
msgstr ""
"Тасдиқи почтаи электронӣ ба пайваст мондани дархостҳо ва фаъолияти "
"хизматрасонӣ бо ҳисоби дуруст кумак мекунад."

#: accounts/templates/accounts/partials/marketplace_sections.html:248
msgid "Are professional offers available now?"
msgstr "Оё ҳоло пешниҳодҳои мутахассисон дастрасанд?"

#: accounts/templates/accounts/partials/marketplace_sections.html:249
msgid ""
"The interface is prepared for offers and bookings. Real offer data will "
